    <scopecontent id="aspace_hzc210590n520as93011873591633">
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>Letters from artist friends, including three letters and a postcard from David Burliuk; 17 from Philip Evergood about visiting Popper, teaching and painting; and one letter from Abraham Walkowitz; and a rough draft and a final copy of I PAINT PEOPLE AND THINGS, a lecture given by Evergood at Hamline University in St. Paul, Minnesota.</p>
    </scopecontent>
    <altformavail id="aspace_hzc210590n530as96186187018379">
